01:23:47.060 --> 01:23:49.010
happening and where
people are actually

01:23:49.010 --> 01:23:53.990
daring to step out and
model that, I think

01:23:53.990 --> 01:23:55.620
we need to turn
our focus to that,

01:23:55.620 --> 01:23:59.076
