01:24:48.567 --> 01:24:49.481
yeah, yeah.

01:24:49.481 --> 01:24:51.064
JUAN CARLOS POLANCO:
It's interesting.

01:24:51.064 --> 01:24:52.460
I come from a world of politics.

01:24:52.460 --> 01:24:54.150
I don't come from
the tech world.

01:24:54.150 --> 01:24:55.490
So this is my life.

01:24:55.490 --> 01:24:56.600
This is what I deal with.

