01:26:49.970 --> 01:26:51.590
then I would find
it easier to believe

01:26:51.590 --> 01:26:53.490
that that's the motivation.

01:26:53.490 --> 01:26:55.790
But it always-- and
not just in the US,

01:26:55.790 --> 01:26:59.630
it's in other countries-- it's
always associated with fear

01:26:59.630 --> 01:27:01.910
mongering, and putting
down certain groups,

01:27:01.910 --> 01:27:04.020
and that they're
dangerous and so on.

01:27:04.020 --> 01:27:05.092
So I mean, that's--

01:27:05.092 --> 01:27:06.508
JUAN CARLOS POLANCO:
I understand.

01:27:06.508 --> 01:27:07.716
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

